OL,3,CAnimal sanctuary facing closure
OL,4,Cdesperately searches for new home
OL,6,FThe lease of the farm and land they
OL,7,Fuse is ending in 2026 and they need to
OL,8,Ffind somewhere else. It is a race
OL,9,Fagainst time.
OL,11,FTrustee Jonathan Gray said they are
OL,12,Flooking for donations and contacts.
OL,13,FOne possibility would involve a share
OL,14,Farrangement.
OL,16,FHe said: "One idea we are looking at
OL,17,Fis to create a limited company that
OL,18,Fwould be used to buy the land that we
OL,19,Fneed. The company would rent the land
OL,20,Fto the sanctuary.
