OL,3,CAnimal sanctuary facing closure
OL,4,Cdesperately searches for new home
OL,6,F"The idea is that we have a share
OL,7,Fissue of around #50 per share. People
OL,8,Fwould basically buy a small piece of
OL,9,Fthe sanctuary. They would become part
OL,10,Fof the Idlewild family."
OL,12,FOf the task ahead he said: "We are not
OL,13,Fgoing to quit. There is too much at
OL,14,Fstake."
OL,16,FSanctuary manager, Kim Barton-Jones
OL,17,Fsaid many of their volunteers have
OL,18,Fadditional needs and mental health
OL,19,Fissues.
