OL,4,Cdesperately searches for new home
OL,6,FShe explained: "We are not only
OL,7,Fworried about what might happen to the
OL,8,Fanimals but many of our volunteers do
OL,9,Fnot leave the house apart from coming
OL,10,Fto Idlewild."
OL,12,FShe said that if they were to find
OL,13,Fsomewhere else the potential for
OL,14,Fdevelopment was huge.
OL,16,FShe added that the fundraising target
OL,17,Fat around half a million pounds was
OL,18,Fbig but it wouldn't deter them.
